00e9cise, mais \u00e9galement plusieurs formats d\u2019annonces display en ad\u00e9quation avec vos objectifs. Dans cet article notre agence Google Ads Display vous propose une analyse des diff\u00e9rents formats d\u2019annonce disponibles ainsi que les pertinences de chacun.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"image-single-wrapper visuel-article text-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/google-display.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Google Display\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/google-display.png 1920w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/google-display-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/google-display-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/google-display-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article article-table-matiere&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc toc\"><p class=\"titre_3\">Table des mati\u00e8res<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Sommaire<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM